#  Be sure to disable 'cpu I386_CPU' && 'cpu I486_CPU' for SMP kernels.
#
#  Check the 'Rogue SMP hardware' section to see if additional options
#   are required by your hardware.
#

# Mandatory:
options 	APIC_IO			# Symmetric (APIC) I/O

